description: Try our easy to follow Prawn & Chicken Stir-Fry recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Prawn & Chicken StirFry Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Pour coconut milk mixture into pan and bring to the boil. Add chicken, rice and spring onion, tossing to combine. Cook for 2 minutes or until heated through. Spoon into bowls and serve topped with cashews, shallots, mint leaves and remaining lime.
